Puppet module: ocsinventory

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages ocsinventory software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include ocsinventory              # Install and run ocsinventory with standard configurations.
include ocsinventory::disable     # Disable ocsinventory service.
include ocsinventory::disableboot # Disable ocsinventory service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include ocsinventory::absent      # Remove ocsinventory package.

DEPENDENCIES:
